40863.title: Modern Family
40863.description: Het huis van de Dunphy's barst uit zijn voegen wanneer Dylans hippiemoeder intrekt en Jerry, de eenzame stiefvader van Claire, op bezoek wil komen. Jay en Gloria proberen Manny te helpen met zijn liefdesverdriet om Sherry.

40864.title: Modern Family
40864.description: Cameron is hoping to keep everyone happy for their annual Christmas dinner as he hides and prepares for his big interview for a head coaching position out of state. Meanwhile, Haley is excited to finally be reunited with wine; and Mitchell is suspicious of Cam's holiday trip to visit his family in Missouri.

40865.title: Modern Family
40865.description: Alex's new company is putting her up at a new luxury apartment with full amenities and a list of high-profile residents that the family is eager to take advantage of, without her knowing. Phil is on a mission to review the restaurant's famous sliders for his food blog, while Mitch and Cam sneak in separately to meet its most famous resident, David Beckham. Meanwhile, Luke and Manny head straight for the gym to try and pick up on older women and end up in some hot water with a few of the residents.

40866.title: Modern Family
40866.description: Phil pays a visit to his dad to make sure he is ok after hearing some concerning news about him. Meanwhile, Jay gives Claire and Mitch a bunch of their old childhood memorabilia that triggers them to reevaluate a long-held story about their first family vacation.

40867.title: Modern Family
40867.description: Mitchell learns a valuable life lesson when Murray, a former resident of the house, shows up unexpectedly. Meanwhile, the Dunphy's old neighbor-turned-tech-titan, Kenneth, comes to visit with a big surprise for Phil. Then, Manny's dad, Javier, shows up with a big opportunity for his son.

40868.title: Modern Family
40868.description: In one last family trip, they head to Paris so Jay can accept a lifetime achievement award in the closet industry, but his old nemesis, Earl Chambers, comes back to haunt him. Meanwhile, Claire has a secret rendezvous in one of the most romantic cities in the world, and Cam's lifelong dream of performing as Fizbo on the streets of Paris is about to become a reality

40869.title: Modern Family
40869.description: Phil en Claire nemen Haley en Dylan mee uit eten om ze ervan te verzekeren dat ze geen slechte ouders zijn.

40870.title: Modern Family
40870.description: Claire mag op sollicitatiegesprek komen voor haar droombaan, maar wordt gedwarsboomd door de lastige trap van Phil.

40872.title: Modern Family
40872.description: Mitchell en Cam beginnen te wennen aan hun nieuwe normaal en Phil en Claire besluiten dat een van de kinderen het huis uit moet om weer controle over het huishouden te krijgen.

40879.title: South Park
40879.description: De meest gênante geheimen van de jongens komen terecht op een bizarre nieuwe roddelwebsite.

40882.title: South Park
40882.description: De jongens komen dicht bij het ontdekken van de waarheid over de eerste Thanksgiving.

40885.title: Family Guy
40885.description: Peter raakt bevriend met een coole, knappe hulpverlener genaamd Stryker Foxx. Helemaal opgaand in z'n nieuwe coolheid dumpt hij Quagmire, Joe en Cleveland.

40888.title: Family Guy
40888.description: In deze aflevering in compilatiestijl wordt Peter ontslagen bij de brouwerij in de kenmerkende stijl van drie bekende Hollywoodregisseurs.

40889.title: Family Guy
40889.description: Als Brian een beledigende tweet stuurt die viral gaat en de overige Griffins ook als paria's worden behandeld, wordt hij gedwongen het huishouden te verlaten.

40893.title: Family Guy
40893.description: In deze speciale Dickens-aflevering zijn Stewie en Brian detectives die een reeks mysterieuze moorden in het victoriaanse Londen moeten oplossen.

40894.title: American Dad!
40894.description: American Dad gaat over patriottische CIA-agent Stan Smith (stem door Seth Macfarlane) en de avonturen van z'n onconventionele gezin in Langley Falls, VA.

40895.title: Hoe Tem Je Een Draak 2
40895.description: Dit vervolg op Hoe Tem Je Een Draak keert terug naar de fantasierijke wereld van Viking Hikkie en zijn trouwe draak Tandloos, die hun krachten moeten bundelen om de vrede te bewaren.

40896.title: Space Jam
40896.description: Get a laugh-loaded glimpse of the future as it's never looked before! See two of the world's greatest legends collide in a brand-new universe! When basketball megastar Michael Jordan teams up with animated icon Bugs Bunny--get ready for Space Jam! Charles Barkley, Patrick Ewing, Daffy Duck, Porky Pig--and many more. The National Basketball Association meets Warner Bros.' Looney Tunes--with Jordan as a live-action hero entering a spectacular animated world. Captured by Bugs Bunny to foil a ghastly gang of space creatures, Jordan must play the basketball game of his life to save the beloved cartoon heroes from a hideous kidnapping scheme. Will Jordan beat the odds and get his Looney new pals out of a real jam? Fasten your seat belts and enter a whole new dimension in entertainment in the wildest, wackiest comic fantasy ever.
